Name: iidxbak
Version: 0.9.3
Description-Content-Type: text/markdown
Requires-Dist: click (==8.0.4)
Requires-Dist: sh (>=1.14.3)
Requires-Dist: oss2 (==2.18.3)

## 本项目用于在centos上备份信息

### 使用步骤
1. mkdir -p ${HOME}/.iidxbak/work && pushd ${HOME}/.iidxbak/work 
2. python3 -m pip install pipenv==2020.11.15
3. pipenv install --index https://pypi.org/simple iidxbak==0.9.1 --skip-lock
3. pipenv run iidxbak --dir_to_bak some_path_to_bak

### config_demo
* 默认软件家目录：${HOME}/.iidxbak/
* 默认配置文件位置：${HOME}/.iidxbak/conf/iidxbak.json
* 默认工作目录：${HOME}/.iidxbak/work/{20231111-1010}/
```json
{
  "public_key": "conf/keys.public.pem",
  "work_dir": "work/",
  "oss_ak_id": "XXXX",
  "oss_ak_secret": "XXXX",
  "oss_ep": "https://oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com",
  "oss_bucket_name": "XXXX",
  "i_node_info": true
}
```

### 项目依赖

> * click==8.1.7
> * sh==2.0.6 
> * oss2==2.18.3

### 环境安装
```shell
# 0. uname -a 
uname -a
# Linux app-001-156 3.10.0-1160.76.1.el7.x86_64 #1 SMP Wed Aug 10 16:21:17 UTC 2022 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux
# 1. sudo yum install -y python3-devel

# 2. ssh -V
ssh -V
# OpenSSH_7.4p1, OpenSSL 1.0.2k-fips  26 Jan 2017

# 3. openssl version
openssl version
# OpenSSL 1.0.2k-fips  26 Jan 2017

# 4. python3 --version
python3 --version
# Python 3.6.8
```

